        <p>This holiday can only be booked over the phone at this time. We have a dedicated team of travel experts who will be able to help you complete your booking over the phone, please give them a call on the following dedicated number:</p>
        <p class="text-center bk-call-us">Call us: <span>0208 183 0501 <!-- @Session["phoneno"] --></span></p>
